title: 1789 Capital Partner on SpaceX IPO
description: Paul Abrahimzadeh, Partner at 1789 Capital and former Citigroup Co-Head of Equity Capital Markets for North America, says 2025 is shaping up as a year of companies going public with a strong backlog, alongside active M&A coming out of Silicon Valley. He speaks with Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on “The Close.” (Source: Bloomberg)
